{
    "id": "aquaria/walstad",
    "title": "Set up a Walstad tank",
    "description": "Create a low-tech planted aquarium using the Walstad method.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/walstad_setup.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/vega.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Hi there! I'm Vega. Ready to build a Walstad tank that can run lean? We'll layer soil, cap it, and plant before we ever reach for livestock.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "stage",
                    "text": "Yes—show me the steps",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "83fe7eee-135e-4885-9ce0-9042b9fb860a",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "98609b23-4811-4275-8d83-ad59a2797753",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "75cec98f-fcf0-4d73-8d31-5a53571317b2",
                            "count": 3
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "62757412-be94-48c0-a1c0-8fad9bdb8c4a",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0704e829-ce72-4c7d-91b0-8a774b11575d",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "c5a7574e-515f-4e9a-83fc-350703131f25",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0564d441-7367-412e-b709-dad770814a39",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "16eb261b-9d93-4aff-ab31-40f6a78d04f1",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "stage",
            "text": "Roll the stand to level ground, place the tank, and lay out soil, gravel, plants, light, and your conditioner with a clean bucket. Keep the intake cords dry.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "condition-bucket-water",
                    "text": "Prep dechlorinated fill water"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "build",
                    "text": "Bucket is dechlorinated and tools are staged",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "71efa72a-8c87-4dc2-8e2c-9119bb28fe50",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "build",
            "text": "Add the soil layer, cap with rinsed gravel, tuck in guppy grass and duckweed, then fill gently with the dechlorinated bucket so you don't blast the substrate. Aim the light for an 8-hour timer.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-walstad-tank",
                    "text": "Layer and plant the Walstad tank"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "thermo",
                    "text": "Substrate settled and plants look secure",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "785fa6f3-bb66-4197-a43f-52fea9cebd48",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "thermo",
            "text": "Dry the outside glass near eye level. Attach the strip thermometer before cycling so you can track swing without dunking probes.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "attach-aquarium-thermometer",
                    "text": "Attach the strip thermometer"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Thermometer is on and readable",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "4e8db808-927f-4ac7-9d1f-1c8400c7f5d7",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Great start. Let the tank settle and test before stocking. Keep feeding the light daily and resist adding fish until ammonia and nitrite stay at zero.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "I'll let it cycle cleanly"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
